00:15:44.220 --> 00:15:45.920
So basically promo
codes is something

00:15:45.920 --> 00:15:48.260
we launched a couple
of months ago,

00:15:48.260 --> 00:15:52.950
and it's the ability for you
to create up to 500 promo codes

00:15:52.950 --> 00:15:57.480
and have a self-serve
promo code campaign.

00:15:57.480 --> 00:15:59.260
Instead of having
to work with Google

00:15:59.260 --> 00:16:02.160
and figure out how to get
promo codes in front of users,

00:16:02.160 --> 00:16:06.340
for up to 500 users, you
can create a promo code

00:16:06.340 --> 00:16:09.530
and send it out so they can
experience your app or part

00:16:09.530 --> 00:16:11.320
of the content for free.

00:16:11.320 --> 00:16:13.070
So this would be really
useful for things

00:16:13.070 --> 00:16:16.790
like, if there's a certain group
of influencers who you want

00:16:16.790 --> 00:16:20.140
to get your app out to, or
a group of let's say parent

00:16:20.140 --> 00:16:22.820
evangelists, or even if there's
a marketing campaign you're

00:16:22.820 --> 00:16:24.752
doing to a target set of users.

00:16:24.752 --> 00:16:26.460
So you can basically
run this on your own

00:16:26.460 --> 00:16:27.590
from the developer console.

00:16:30.250 --> 00:16:31.945
And then store
listening experiments--

00:16:31.945 --> 00:16:33.570
actually I won't ask
about this since I

00:16:33.570 --> 00:16:36.370
do know that 70% of
