00:16:56.690 --> 00:17:00.500
that kids love icons and
colors, and that's typically

00:17:00.500 --> 00:17:03.670
the first thing they gravitate
towards when they select

00:17:03.670 --> 00:17:05.700
an app to purchase or download.

00:17:05.700 --> 00:17:08.230
And so getting that right
is really important.

00:17:08.230 --> 00:17:10.484
One of our top
partners, Baby First,

00:17:10.484 --> 00:17:12.400
experimented with a
